description: Lists all asset bundle import jobs that have taken place in the last 14 days. Jobs created more than 14 days ago are deleted forever and are not returned. If you are using the same job ID for multiple jobs, ListAssetBundleImportJobs only returns the most recent job that uses the repeated job ID.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that the import jobs were executed in.

nested_items.name: AssetBundleImportJobSummaryList
nested_items.description: A list of import job summaries.

nested_items.name: JobStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the import job.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the import job.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that the import job was created.

nested_items.name: AssetBundleImportJobId
nested_items.description: The ID of the job. This ID is unique while the job is running. After the job is completed, you can reuse this ID for another job.

nested_items.name: FailureAction
nested_items.description: The failure action for the import job.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the response.
